OS_Byte 220  Read/Write escape character
#Parent OS_ByteIndex
=>	R0 =	220 (&DC)
	R1 =	EOR value
	R2 =	AND value

<=	R0 preserved
	R1 =	previous value
	R2 corrupted
                                                  
This call reads or sets the character that causes an escape condition when read from the input stream. The default is 27 (generated by the escape key).
#Line
See <PRM 1, page 889=>PRM-1:889>
